    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist Now!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Toilet Labs, where Human testing is back in fashion!</h2><br>Kidnapped and trapped in a bizarre lab, navigate through challenging toilet-themed puzzles to reach the ultimate throne. Manoeuvre fans, throw plungers, and even manipulate gravity to conserve pee. Confront the eccentric founder, Mr. Latrine and find the secret rooms and the messages he has left for you. Choose your destiny with two endings – ascend to the coveted porcelain throne, or team up with Mr. Latrine to explosively escape the facility. It is up to you to answer nature's call in this quest for bathroom supremacy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pee</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/ef5060eac3674a896fcc435c431409e7.poster.avif?t=1725296972\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/ef5060eac3674a896fcc435c431409e7.webm?t=1725296972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/ef5060eac3674a896fcc435c431409e7.mp4?t=1725296972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pee your way through the labs. The more you get in the toilet the higher your score.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Toilet Themed Puzzles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/4b1a806100ffebedde097124accde271.avif?t=1725296972\" width=616 height=316 /></span><br>Find the solutions to 20 hand crafted puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interact with the Environment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/3a6ac15e74191856d81bd3fd837449f1.poster.avif?t=1725296972\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/3a6ac15e74191856d81bd3fd837449f1.webm?t=1725296972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/3a6ac15e74191856d81bd3fd837449f1.mp4?t=1725296972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use buckets, plungers, fans, gravity and more to solve each level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the Truth</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/f516b4f6527b93ad09ad0194b3a9d5b1.avif?t=1725296972\" width=616 height=312 /></span><br>Explore the secret areas and collect all the Golden Plungers to find out why you are here and how to escape.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351110/extras/17c5b748dbcd6386ac8f0ed1bd71a8fa.avif?t=1725296972\" width=616 height=366 /></span><br>Confront the final lab in an epic conclusion to determine your fate.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist Now!</h2><br>Approx. 1-2 hours of playtime. I have not tested PlayStation controllers, they may or may not work.",
